Help Type: topic
Topic: recipe

Recipes

Create an archive from Markdown:
  spinedigest create book.sdpub ./book.md
  cat article.md | spinedigest create article.sdpub --input-format markdown

Queue derived data:
  spinedigest queue add book.sdpub --chapter 3 --task reading-graph --accept-cost
  spinedigest queue add book.sdpub --chapter 3 --task summary --accept-cost
  spinedigest queue add book.sdpub --chapter 3 --task knowledge-graph --accept-cost

Search and open objects:
  spinedigest search book.sdpub "恩典 婴儿洗礼"
  spinedigest get book.sdpub wikigraph://chunk/123
  spinedigest related book.sdpub wikigraph://entity/Q162593
  spinedigest evidence book.sdpub wikigraph://triple/Q162593/discusses/Q9476
  spinedigest pack book.sdpub wikigraph://entity/Q162593 --budget 5000

Export:
  spinedigest export book.sdpub --output-format markdown --output out.md

Transform without an archive:
  cat chapter.txt | spinedigest transform --input-format txt --output-format markdown
